name: Touchdown Wars:  Where There Is No Off-Season!
blurb: Fantasy Football meets browser-based gaming.  Manage your players & franchise to compete online against friends.

rewards.reward: A personal Thank You from Rival Studios and $10 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks) to spend on creating a player or team, equipment, etc.

A personal Thank You from Rival Studios, receive $20 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks) (to spend on creating a player or team, equipment, etc.), and your name in the credits as a donor for this project.
(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $40 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks), receive one Kickstarter Exclusive in-game item, and full access into our closed beta.
(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $60 worth of Touchdown Wars game money and a limited edition Touchdown Wars t-shirt.

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $100 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks), receive 3 kickstarter exclusive in-game items, full access to our Touchdown Wars community updates, and a Touchdown Wars Coffee Mug.

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $150 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks) and name 3 unique Touchdown Wars computer players, select their position, and allocate attributes to create a superstar for your team!

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $200 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks), your name in the credits as an official Bronze level sponsor for the Touchdown Wars project, a Limited Edition Touchdown Wars T-Shirt, you get to add 1 city choice for teams to select in Touchdown Wars, and you get to work with our graphic artist to create 1 player profile character for the Touchdown Wars game.

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $500 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks), your name in the credits as an official Silver level sponsor of the Touchdown Wars project, one Limited Edition 24"x36" Touchdown Wars poster, you get to add 3 city choices for teams to select in Touchdown Wars, and you get to work with our graphic artist to create one coach profile character and attributes for the Touchdown Wars game.

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus $1000 worth of Touchdown Wars game money (Fan Bucks), your name in the credits as an official Gold level sponsor of the Touchdown Wars project, one of each Touchdown Wars game apparel, items, and accessories, you get to create your own custom stadium with our graphic artist to be used in the official Touchdown Wars game, you get to work with our graphic artist to create 3 team logos for users to choose as their official team logo in Touchdown Wars, and access to game progress updates from the CEO.

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus your name in the credits as a Platinum level sponsor of the Touchdown Wars project, you get to create 5 in-game purchase items with our graphic artist that will be sold in the game store for Touchdown Wars, a copy of our digital soundtrack, and you can add 10 city choices for Touchdown Wars teams to select.

(All of the Above)\r\nPlus your name listed in the credits as an Executive Producer of Touchdown Wars.  This will provide you with behind the scenes access to our development process and regular meetings with our entire project team via Skype.
